what: American Community Survey population data — acs
title: American Community Survey population data — acs
text: data sets contain population data Kansas City, Missouri, sourced US Census Bureau's American Community Survey (ACS). 1-year ACS data sets, summary level Kansas City . 5-year ACS data sets, summary levels include city, county, census tract, census block group, ZIP code tabulation area (ZCTA). Data sets downloaded data.census.gov using get_kc_pop(). See Guidance Data Users information use ACS data.
